  "texts": [
    "The MultiSenseBadminton dataset 75 is available on figshare.",
    "The collected dataset was multimodal dataset that involved 25 participants of varying skill levels and had a total duration of 1,403 minutes (Mean = 56 minutes, SD = 7.48 minutes).",
    "In addition to physiological data such as EMG and gaze, the dataset contains behavioral data such as foot pressure and joint movement, as well as video data for sensor visualization and annotation data.",
    "The dataset also includes data summary files and survey data, in addition to sensor data.",
    "All the data files are accessible on a hierarchical database, which facilitates navigation and retrieval of specific data."
  ],
